{"tid":1614571,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"PayPal 正式進入中國市場 成首間外國支付平台","createTime":"2019-10-02T23:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:45:01.000Z","uid":284699,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d9ad740640697f13e4a3a9eb46a56e5e7dc6fae","tid":1614571,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:24:39.000Z","msg":"近日，以美國作總部的第三方支付服務商 PayPal 亦成功打入中國市場，成為首個在內地運作的外國支付平台。9 月 30 日，國付寶（Gopay）在其官方網站上宣布，中國人民銀行正式批准 PayPal 通過旗下美銀寶住息技術（上海）有限公司收購國付寶（gopay） 70% 的股權，成為國付寶的大股東，成功進入中國電子支付服務市場。<br />\n<br />\nPayPal 成功進軍內地電子支付服務市場<br />\n成為首個外國支付平台<br />\nPayPal 旗下公司收購了 國付寶（Gopay）70% 的股權<br />\n<br />\nPayPal 自與 eBay 分家後，一直想近軍大陸市場，但礙於沒有內地支付牌照而處處碰壁。今次 PayPal 收購的國付寶，原本的大股東是海航集團全資控股的子公司 &mdash; 北京知融信達科技公司。<br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2464285\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2464285&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7G9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=536472d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2464285</a>"},{"pid":"88e777aeb52b1c9254dcdd04437f6f78ce5759f8","tid":1614571,"uid":130996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:35:53.000Z","msg":"好奇會點運作"},{"pid":"2234fbe062c44a7904e55b475fac8b8ecc411b17","tid":1614571,"uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:39:27.000Z","msg":"同paypal互通之後<br />\n平民可以走資 政府又可以印銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4412ecdcd377ade603ac1c989e1767e74b677298","tid":1614571,"uid":35457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:44:48.000Z","msg":"碌假銀聯既走資時代開始了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69778ad1bc2cb18b60a52111865ecfc7691ef30","tid":1614571,"uid":76776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T23:51:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22dbbfde0a036f05d2789fc064692fa71b51f77f","tid":1614571,"uid